<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>I agree that a chanter should not be capable of soloing a level 65 mob, one which many groups of 6 people have a hard time with. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
<br>
This is where I agree with both of you. I don't have a problem with the fact that mobs can be charmed to create monster mobs, alot of us don't and we don't blame CoD for that. We blame the scaling of the power of mobs in PoP. I don't have a major problem that you <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>can</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> get an aa every 20 minutes. As you pointed out, there are other classes that can do that. Wizards quadding, for example. The people that have a problem with this are jealous that we can't do that, of which I am one fo them. I don't think CoD should be nerfed for the XP gain however.<br>
<br>
However, as long as mobs are available, I'm sure some enchanter somewhere will find somewhere to kill named with one charmed mob. IE) Sleepwalker with a charmed razorfiend (Not sure if it's been done before, but a suggestion).<br>
<br>
Manaburn wasn't bad in itself, but when they used it to kill named dragons that whole guilds couldn't kill, people yelled for a nerf, and it happened for almost a year. <br>
<br>
This is the same for CoD. No one really cared about it before enchanters posted that they could kill BoT named with it, that they could run ahead of groups killing in a wing in BoT and kill the named from their camp. No one cared untill enchanters went overboard on CoD and started killing this crap.<br>
<br>
We come down to two soloutions. Nerf something when somewhere is found where an enchanter can kill something he/she shouldn't be able to, or nerf CoD in itself. If you could find a reasonable soloution to these problems, then I'm all for them, but keeping CoD as it is right now, and/or keeping the zones as they are right now, is just not right, ecspecially BoT. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.power3d.com/Arch/member_inv.asp?member_id=263"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://hobie.homestead.com/files/Nukeb.JPG" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
